{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Prohibit companies from delivering leaflets to houses until the lockdown ends.",
        "additional_details": "It is not fair that a lot of people have lost their jobs and others did isolate their selves voluntarily to find that these irresponsible companies sending the potentially contaminated flyers to their houses. Kids usually run to the door when they hear the door mail slot has sounded to get the colourful cards.\r\n\r\nLeaflet distributors should stop their activities until further notice from the government. and take this seriously as their workers are not protecting their selves from the infection.",
        "background": "We, as a lot of people, have locked ourselves indoor to protect us and others from the spread of Coronavirus. It seems that the fact that people are at home encouraged treaders to take advantage and send leaflets for ads. Three days in a row my kids get the leaflets from the door.",
